Package: RECP
Title: Rank Energy Change Point Test for Multivariate Data
Version: 1.0.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jiaqi", "Li", , "ljq0814nana@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides nonparametric methods for detecting and locating a single
    change point in multivariate data sequences. The package implements a rank
    energy statistic constructed from multivariate ranks defined via optimal
    transport theory. The asymptotic null distribution is distribution-free,
    enabling universal rejection thresholds across different sample sizes.
    Two testing procedures are provided: a permutation-based test (REp) and
    a test based on simulating the limiting spectral distribution (REs).
    The methods are robust to heavy-tailed distributions and are accompanied
    by theoretical guarantees for change point location estimation.
